##How to install octopress theme

```html octopress
cd octopress
git clone git@github.com:tommy351/Octopress-Theme-Slash.git .themes/slash
rake install['slash']
rake generate
```
各种主题：<https://github.com/imathis/octopress/wiki/3rd-Party-Octopress-Themes>
